data.description: Split 2-bedroom condo with an inviting living room. This condo highlights an up-dated kitchen with sleek stainless-steel appliances, solid quartz countertops, white cabinetry, track lighting, and an accessible breakfast bar. Each bedroom boasts of its own private bath. Outside, there is an oversized patio, close assigned covered parking, and quick access to the pool. This Community offers fantastic amenities: 3 swimming pools, a hot tub, a fitness center, and more!
